# Vendored third-party Agent Skills. Every skill under .agents/skills/ is
# installed from someone else's repo (mattpocock/skills, anthropics/skills,
# microsoft/playwright-cli, nexu-io/open-design, vercel-labs/skills) and is
# pinned by .agents/.skill-lock.json, which records each source URL and folder
# hash. The lockfile IS tracked, so the set is reproducible; the payload is not
# ours to redistribute from a public repo, and it is 6 MB (5.6 MB of that is 54
# .ttf files vendored by canvas-design).
.agents/skills/

# Claude Code's per-machine permission allowlist — a local override by design,
# and it accumulates one-off `Bash(rm ...)` grants specific to this box.
.claude/settings.local.json
